key "scientific_working_group_on_dna_analysis_methods_swgdam_2020"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Training in the factors involved in DNA-TPPR has been identified as a key requirement.
 Van Oorschot et al (2017) found that there was a lack of consistency in understanding factors involved in DNA-TPPR across individuals and organisations 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "van_oorschot_need_2017"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 A review of DNA transfer from the same group in 2019 identified that in order to carry out activity level proposition evaluation 
